§7§oThis table requires starlight to work. It needs sky access. The closer it is to midnight, the higher the starlight.

This table works best at high y level, the higher you are, the higher the starlight. There are special chunks where starlight is higher, the resonator will lets you find them at night.

If a recipe does not have enough starlight, it will not show up as craftable in the table.

Right click the table with a resonating wand to start the recipe.
